    <detaileddescription>
<para>Base class for platform-dependent code handling touchpad events</para>
<para>If you want to add touchpad gesture support on your platform, inherit this class, extend the <computeroutput><ref refid="group__GeneralGroup_1ga28e436c01d418ee35f2c34370fac094d" kindref="member">TouchpadController::initialize</ref></computeroutput> method and call the corresponding methods on the touchpad events. </para>
